layout: post
title: "${1:Title}"
date: ${2:YYYY-MM-DD} 12:00
comments: true
categories: 
- ProfHacker$3
tags: 
- ProfHacker$4
---

*[This post originally appeared at [ProfHacker][].]*

  [ProfHacker]: $5

$0
endsnippet

